What a phenomenal concept. Not only do they have excellent sandwiches, salads, muffins & a Starbucks,  all proceeds go to the UMOM family homeless shelter.  All the employees are residents training to be baristas & culinary workers & will have marketable job skills when they transition to living independently. Please support this place. Not only will you enjoy the food,  but you'll be making a huge contribution to our community.

